column5: I DIDN'T catch this but got to hold it for the picture and was she heavy and I am not holding it at arms length but as close to me as I could without touching my suit.    vance   well i did something wrong back to square one  that didn't work either can someone tell me what i am doing wrong   Thanks Bill I couldn't get a big pic like you did to come up but this is ok.
Vance, the URL goes inbetween the IMG tags...   You've got http:// on the outside of the tag..
